{"tid":1379972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作者：支持成立獨立調查委員會的人，要問自己幾個問題","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:36:53.000Z","uid":260035,"like":127,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a795273fa0496788761a888786c7796fa2b4b9f2","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2560564017327054&amp;id=972393926144079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2560564017327054%26id%3D972393926144079&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=3d3495f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2560564017327054&amp;id=972393926144079</a><br />\n<br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會的人，要問自己幾個問題：<br />\n<br />\n這個委員會有沒有權力宣判罪在王志民、盧偉聰和林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力調查中聯辦干政？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力決定解散內閣（即行政會議）？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力刑事檢控盧偉聰和林鄭、轉介司法審判？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力將虐待市民的警員革職？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力監督警隊內部改革，甚至遣散警隊？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n口講話「獨立調查」，但誰委任誰去查呢？大家心知肚明，最後只是監警會的翻版。<br />\n<br />\n他們將會在一年半載後對市民說：我們強烈譴責xxxx，建議政府xxxx。建議咋，最終個決定權，仍然在中聯辦和特首手上。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋會深切反省同檢討，積極回應市民訴求&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n倫敦的「獨立人民法庭」去年裁定中共活摘囚犯器官是犯下「反人類罪行」，然後呢？中共受到甚麼懲罰？政體罪成，又有誰可懲罰政體？<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳都講到明：成立獨立委員會可以幫政府買些時間。<br />\n<br />\n買時間幹甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n瓦解抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n但我都支持成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n條件是，70個調查委員都必須由全港直選產生，成為當然議員，取締功能組別。<br />\n<br />\n刑不上大夫，也刑不上黨官，甚至刑不上幾萬個警察，試問查來幹甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n你會要求李鵬成立獨立調查委員會調查天安門事件嗎？<br />\n<br />\n永遠只有新政府上台，才有權查前朝。習近平有權查李鵬，文在寅有權查朴槿惠。<br />\n<br />\n邊個有權查林鄭同中聯辦？答案得兩個：一係你叫中紀委干預香港內政，一係成立民選政府港人審港。<br />\n<br />\n只可惜，很快就沒有機會查盧偉聰了&mdash;&mdash;因為他在11月將會脫離港共政權，投奔中共體系。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"dc8022124a18b4771c27e9dcaaef36357babcc2d","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b51ad23fa4ecf4e449734ad8f8763dcff918591a","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:52:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1eb8071ed28e7a71a2fc0c821d1b1361654fc7b","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"請全文讀完 看內容"},{"pid":"e3cf027bc403302c68d0257b8b377b7bfdd0094c","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9335c2b95593446b6a01e57773697c7bbd8fcf33","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d1885ac6bddc1a8ddf19b7b774d6023da297d062","tid":1379972,"uid":238046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:56:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30f3b8b7b33e2c2b172c8d8fc208db2f25fb6920","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bb56ed22f3ced4b377ffd53da0ed5ebf5e801ac","tid":1379972,"uid":76366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8e127115371fd09491649b1c3c43c932505923","tid":1379972,"uid":61494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"同其他目標冇衝突"},{"pid":"a601d6243d2d1860e122b7643654fcf36a2f8827","tid":1379972,"uid":144156,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"其實呢個真係悲哀既事實，根本冇民主冇認受性既獨立調查，係唔會還到人民一個公道"},{"pid":"e4f71b76595f44d9672ffe6f844c1475c91de9c8","tid":1379972,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1023820faaabebd0cb464e5ffd9dd63853cd9a15","tid":1379972,"uid":50663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"Sad but true. 但都要做 五大訴求點都要達成"},{"pid":"1a48caad895e40f79bb3ef883d8e7725dabe4624","tid":1379972,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【緊急！置頂！】三毛最新風向：反對成立獨立調查委員會</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abanHDU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abanHDU</a>"},{"pid":"93f8b24eb49a5a5e66fe618d3c4eae52a13e1fbd","tid":1379972,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"【緊急！置頂！】三毛最新風向：反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370130</a>"},{"pid":"e6c1291d4f68552138835531e5062b031dd2871b","tid":1379972,"uid":232766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:10:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">【重要】反對/押後成立獨立調查委員會：邏輯謬誤詳解</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372617</a>"},{"pid":"be4b17f5835a520d9bf4ce5f5352f763181b4861","tid":1379972,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"時代革命<br />\n香港獨立"},{"pid":"284942b04a664ea96792be04c2a0cb2ce79e7db9","tid":1379972,"uid":41209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:14:40.000Z","msg":"又嚟非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a398bac04749f9c75bcfc5184e9c2b3d93058f1","tid":1379972,"uid":280867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02127ac3244cc660447621195b71fce903869a3e","tid":1379972,"uid":232766,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:16:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>大家請認清兩個事實：係邊個話「有我一日都唔會成立獨立調查委員會」？又係邊個組織（其實係員佐級協會）不斷出信強烈反對成立委員會？依家突然吹風話要放棄成立調查委員會，究竟係幫咩人解圍？大家一諗就知。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7eadeeae234324d062e382280d7049a0e60970b0","tid":1379972,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"一係雙普選，一係港獨"},{"pid":"cfec4bbb42571371eb0cd6eb9d26d037c6e3a201","tid":1379972,"uid":189507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"可以走就走，一係就做羊仔，不問世事到終老。<br />\n不過到時唔好話冇錢，政苦唔會照顧尐廢老。"},{"pid":"41b1f02da226af006c8a7eb59cc8b426aa1f9e13","tid":1379972,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無知</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 調查委員會從來唔係檢控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有普選都一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 有權傳召官員作供，應該冇限級數<br />\n王志民就未必得<br />\n被召唔可以唔回<br />\n<br />\n等到有普選<br />\n講緊至少7年<br />\n乜撚野證據都冇哂<br />\n所有人應你一句唔記得就可以甩身<br />\n<br />\n要救義士<br />\n係要盡快召開獨立調查<br />\n挖差佬衰野<br />\n先有機會特赥<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查唔係完美<br />\n但好過監警會100倍<br />\n你唔成立獨立調查<br />\n就係差佬玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7453c5034e4e251fc21c56f09e44a5ede027049a","tid":1379972,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"雙普選固然係五大訴求當中嘅終極目標，<br />\n呢點不容置疑。<br />\n<strong>但係成立獨立調查委員會絕對比雙普選更有迫切性。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我哋兩樣都要同時爭取，缺一不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>越遲成立獨立調查委員會，<br />\n林鄭同黑警就有越多時間銷毀罪證、<br />\n佢哋要為事件負上刑責嘅機會就越渺茫。</strong></span><br />\n所以要盡快成立。<br />\n<br />\n有心人近日不斷陰啲陰啲吹風，<br />\n話我哋應該等到有雙普選先成立調查委員會，<br />\n或者我哋要改為爭取短期無可能達到嘅「重組警隊」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢啲言論客觀效果只係幫林鄭同黑警解困，<br />\n為佢哋爭取時間銷毀罪證。</strong></span><br />\n因為實行雙普選閒閒地都要兩三年，<br />\n到時咩罪證都會無哂，證人都未必搵得齊，點查？<br />\n另外，「重組警隊」亦無法律追訴效力，<br />\n林鄭同黑警咪可以逍遙法外？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>請大家一定要小心呢啲言論。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我哋要做嘅嘢係</ins></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 嚴守五大訴求，缺一不可。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 當中關於警隊嘅訴求，唔可以單單係「追究警隊濫權」或「重組警隊」，而係一定要包括「成立獨立調查委員會」徹查成件事、要令犯錯嘅人負上刑責！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 當委員會成立，我哋一定要確保其組成一定要有有公信力嘅非建制成員，<ins>否則我哋絕不收貨</ins>！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家大家都攰，我唔敢長篇大論阻大家休息。<br />\n但如果你哋仲有精力，<br />\n我寫咗另外一篇長文詳細說明箇中理由同三毛嘅邏輯謬誤: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372617\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372617</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">我哋要記住，五大訴求當中，<br />\n得「成立獨立調查委員會」先有「攻擊力」、<br />\n先可以將呢班罪犯繩之以法、<ins>令對家蝕入肉</ins>！</span><br />\n<br />\n所以有心人千方百計都想阻止，<br />\n但我哋一定唔可以俾林鄭同黑警咁就過骨！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>延伸閱讀</strong></ins><br />\n1. 我兩日前嘅原 post:<br />\n【緊急！置頂！】三毛最新風向：反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370130\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370130</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 另一篇長文解釋點解獨立調查委員會咁重要同迫切：<br />\n【重要】反對/押後成立獨立調查委員會：邏輯謬誤詳解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372617\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372617</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>事關重大，我哋要俾多啲人知等大家提防，請推。</strong><br />\n<br />\n【重要】「成立獨立調查委員會」絕對比「雙普選」及「重組警隊」更有迫切性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38d018d4569da4385d18cdf2a584928675e3f301","tid":1379972,"uid":232766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"41b1f02da226af006c8a7eb59cc8b426aa1f9e13","tid":1379972,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無知</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 調查委員會從來唔係檢控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有普選都一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 有權傳召官員作供，應該冇限級數<br />\n王志民就未必得<br />\n被召唔可以唔回<br />\n<br />\n等到有普選<br />\n講緊至少7年<br />\n乜撚野證據都冇哂<br />\n所有人應你一句唔記得就可以甩身<br />\n<br />\n要救義士<br />\n係要盡快召開獨立調查<br />\n挖差佬衰野<br />\n先有機會特赥<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查唔係完美<br />\n但好過監警會100倍<br />\n你唔成立獨立調查<br />\n就係差佬玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"巴打請考慮有需要時開新 post 以正視聽。三毛越來越急，可能上面落重 order，呢個時候我哋好易被蒙蔽。"}]}